metadata.name: DREAMING by Lawrence Lee #1/9
metadata.description:
My most creative time is that freewheeling period between sleep and wakefulness when my brain remains disengaged from reality (dreaming) and ready to make new and unexpected connections (DREAMING). This is the all-too-brief time when dreams finally make sense and actually change the world.

__________________

**This NFT was created especially for the [READERS MEME of The NFT Magazine.](https://www.thenftmag.io/04-issue-2k23/)**

With this NFT, you can access the exclusive READERS CLUB to read the magazine and participate in the "Readers Gallery" Drop.
